reviewText: My old Sleepless in Seattle was on VCR tape and got eaten by the machine.  This new DVD with the 2nd DVD of "A League if Their Own" in the same package and at such a great "prime" price, was too good of a deal to pass up.  Both DVDs arrived via USPS ahead of the delivery date.  I highly recommend if you like Tom Hanks- then buy them.
